Money Stuff =0A Market crashes usually have the same mechanism. People like=
 a thing, so they =0Abuy it, so it goes up. More people like it, so they bu=
y more of =0A=0A=0A =0A<https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/authors/ARbTQlRLR=
